STATE of North Carolina
v.
Shane ANDERSON. No. 691P05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. January 26, 2006. Shane Anderson, Pro Se. William Hart, Senior Deputy Attorney General, Ronald L. Moore, District Attorney, for State.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 13th day of December 2005 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Superior Court, Buncombe County, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 26th day of January 2006."
